categories: Category:Military officers of the Sith Empire

nodes.text: Tabrex was a sergeant of the Sith Empire during the Galactic War. Part of Katha Niar's team send to Makeb to secure its reserves of Isotope-5, Tabrex accompanied Sith Lord Cytharat in his assault on the Stronghold One. During the mission, Tabrex was killed by the InterStellar Regulators.
